.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, family, romance, sports
House: futuristic, art-deco, townhouse, cottage, ranch-style, cape-cod
1. the cottage house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
4. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the cottage house##1
6. the art-deco house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the cape-cod house##1
8. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
9. the person watching action movies is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | romance | disaster | sports | family     | drama  |
| House           | townhouse | art-deco    | futuristic      | cape-cod  | cottage | ranch-style |

