.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
6 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, chess, snooker, monopoly, canasta
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, british, chinese, colombian, german, polish
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing chess is on the right of the german##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the polish##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the british##1
7. the colombian is on the far right##1
8. the chinese is the person playing snooker##1
9. the person playing chess is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Game   | snooker   | canasta   | monopoly      | backgammon | bridge  | chess   |
| Nationality   | chinese | polish | argentine | british   | german | colombian |

