.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, hiking, singing, traveling, woodworking
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, tea, mirinda, 7up, lemonade
 1. the person drinking tea is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking | baking | traveling | filmmaking | hiking  |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | mirinda  | tea  | water | 7up      | iced-tea |

