3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the fan of country##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the fan of pop##1
6. the fan of disco is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
9. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | dubstep    | country | indie     | disco   | folk     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice | hot-chocolate | tea | lemonade | cola |

