The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skateboarding, volleyball, golf, swimming, baseball, sailing
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Pet         | dog       | turtle     | horse | guinea-pig | snake | chinchilla |
| Sport   | volleyball | baseball | sailing | golf     | skateboarding  | swimming       |

