.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: bus, scooter, subway, bike, helicopter, van
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, ice-hockey, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the person driving the van##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the van##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Transport   | van | bus  | helicopter     | subway    | scooter  | bike          |
| Sport         | golf  | biathlon | ice-hockey | volleyball | rugby | weightlifting |

