2. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the van is the person who likes aquamarine##1
5. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes black##1
8. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
9. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
