.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cranberry, kiwi, onion, peach, peas
The people have 6 different hobbies: drawing, collecting, fishing, traveling, puzzles, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| Hobby   | collecting   | drawing | sudoku | puzzles | fishing | traveling |

