.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, lemonade, mirinda, tea
There 6 different types of food: plum, nectarine, pineapple, lime, grapefruit, carrot
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person eating nectarine is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the person eating lime##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | tea    | 7up     | juice | almond-milk | lemonade | mirinda   |
| Food        | carrot | lime | grapefruit | pineapple   | plum    | nectarine |

